# AudioDebugPanelSystem

## Purpose
Renders an ImGui "Audio" panel with master/sound/music volume sliders seeded from the current
`AudioVolumeSingletonComponent`. When a slider changes it emits a `SetAudioVolumeRequestOneFrameComponent`
carrying the new master/sound/music triplet so the engine updates the live volumes. Returns early when
the volume singleton is absent or when no ImGui context exists (the Testing build pushes no ImGui layer).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| AudioVolumeSingletonComponent | read | Seeds the sliders with the current volumes |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SetAudioVolumeRequestOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | Emitted when a slider value changes |
